WEBVTT

00:00.500 --> 00:04.500
Welcome to the Inspections tutorial.

00:05.700 --> 00:14.700
Create an inspection. Enter the job details, location, and claim type.

00:15.700 --> 00:24.700
Capture evidence. Upload photos, add annotations, and record moisture readings right in the app.

00:25.700 --> 00:34.700
Sign off. Both client and technician add digital signatures with automatic timestamps.

00:35.700 --> 00:44.700
Submit. The inspection auto-generates a report, exports to PDF, and publishes to the client portal.
